  <article role="article" class="group"><div class="inner">
      <div class="intro">
          <p>You may have to pay back some or all of your Child Benefit if:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>your income after tax is £50,000 or more</li>
            <li>you’re the highest earner in your household</li>
          </ul>

          <p>The calculator will give you an estimate of how much you’ll have to pay back. It will also tell you how and when you’ll have to pay it back.</p>

          <h2>Which tax year do you want to get an estimate for?</h2>
          <p>The tax year runs from 6 April to 5 April the following year.</p>

          <div class="get-started">
            <a rel="nofollow" href="/child-benefit-tax-calculator/process_form?year=2012" class="big button">2012 to 2013</a>
            <a rel="nofollow" href="/child-benefit-tax-calculator/process_form?year=2013" class="big button">2013 to 2014</a>
          </div>
      </div>
